Sentencas: A composite double layer cathode of La0.6Sr0.4Co0.8Fe0.2O3-delta/La0.8Sr0.2FeO3-delta (LSCF/LSF) was successfully fabricated by infiltration method to accelerate the sluggish oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) processes.
Titulo: High performance yttria-stabilized zirconia based intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with double nano layer composite cathode

Sentencas: In this composite cathode, both LSF and LSCF layers are uniformly distributed on Yttria-stabilized Zirconia (YSZ) scaffold by optimizing the infiltrating solution components.
Titulo: High performance yttria-stabilized zirconia based intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with double nano layer composite cathode

Sentencas: LSF serves as a protective layer between LSCF and YSZ.
Titulo: High performance yttria-stabilized zirconia based intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with double nano layer composite cathode

Sentencas: The introduction of the LSCF exterior layer has greatly improved cell performance compared with the cell with sole LSF cathode.
Titulo: High performance yttria-stabilized zirconia based intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with double nano layer composite cathode

Sentencas: At 600 degrees C, the maximum power density of the cell with LSCF/LSF/YSZ composite cathode reaches up to 0.559 W cm(-2).
Titulo: High performance yttria-stabilized zirconia based intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with double nano layer composite cathode

Sentencas: The evolution of the cathode polarization resistance verifies that the ORR activity has been greatly enhanced.
Titulo: High performance yttria-stabilized zirconia based intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with double nano layer composite cathode

Sentencas: Therefore, the results indicate that the high cell performance at intermediate temperatures can be obtained by adopting the LSCF cathode into YSZ-based SOFCs using protective layer and that the infiltration method is a practical way for constructing electrode.
Titulo: High performance yttria-stabilized zirconia based intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells with double nano layer composite cathode
